### START: aiConstitution project-specific
# Per SPEC.md §15: audit interaction JSONL is local-only, never tracked.
audit/interactions/*.jsonl
audit/interactions/*.jsonl.gz

# Per hooks/patterns.json: local pattern extensions are user-private.
hooks/patterns.local.json
hooks/command-wrappers.local.toml

# Transient lockfile (concurrent-op guard).
.lock

# bin/ and dist/ are gitignored above (lines 213, 214). The repo
# now ships ZERO files under bin/ — what was previously there is
# embedded into the `ai` binary at build time (see
# src/cmd/ai/embed/) and extracted to ~/.ai/bin/ at install time
# via `ai hooks install command-wrappers`. Same story for the
# repo-root hooks/ tree: replaced by src/cmd/ai/embed/hooks/ +
# `ai hooks install`.

# Per SPEC.md §15: ~/.config/aiConstitution/ is never in-repo, but
# guard against accidents.
.config/aiConstitution/

# Goreleaser ancillary logs.
goreleaser-*.log
### END: aiConstitution project-specific
